# editreadme


step 1:first of all to run this code you will to install python
step 2:all the files in the zip file are written in python
step 3:download the zip file
step 4:un-zip the zip file
step 5:in the zip file, there is a file called entertainment.py, python file
step 6:open the entertainment.py file in any IDE which can run python files
step 7:when we run the entertainment.py file, a window pops up showing movies 
step 8:when someone presses on a movie then the movie trailer and details of the movie pops up
